Package eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.block.structuring

Class Summary
FromCollection Converts the elements of the collection into a new structure.
FromMap Converts the key-value pairs via the two XPath expressions into a new structure.
Join Join two objects structurally and return the new structure.
Singleton Creates a collection with a single element.
SingletonMap Creates a map with a single key-value pair.
ToCollection Uses the given XPath expression to generate the elements of the resulting collection from the structure of the input value.
ToMap Uses the XPath expressions to create the key-value pairs from the source value and convert it into the standard map representation.
Transform Transform the given type via the supplied XSLT transformation and return the new structure.
Unwrap Extracts elements from a collection and dispatches them one-by-one.
Wrap Create a collection from the inputs.
